{"id": 2174, "genre": 1001, "title": "社交网络给你的亲密关系带来过哪些额外的麻烦？", "description": "情人节到了，来口沁人心脾的负能量？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 1628, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180210174624vrRXEfaJtlQHMK8W.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-02-14T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 265223, "content": "因为跟别人太亲密，女朋友跟我分手了。现在很后悔。过完年想办法挽回", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 124537}, {"id": 265224, "content": "亲朋在好友在微信上给你发信息，但我并不想一天到晚都看着微信", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253254}, {"id": 265229, "content": "有事说事，没事瞎聊什么～", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262409}, {"id": 265236, "content": "我真的只是单纯不想发朋友圈，真不是怕我前女友看见", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262439}, {"id": 291606, "content": "不管对方是谁 都只能做到平日的交谈 而不能完成真正的交心了.", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1389178}, {"id": 265245, "content": "一个病人前两天在门诊挂号开住院登记证，由于没有床位，等不了了，上来要求取消住院登记，并把挂号费退到她医保卡里。\n，否则谁会为了10元钱巴巴的跑上来理论呢，\n我一向不带钱在身上，今天又只有我一个人值班，想用微信转给她，可惜她玩不来微信，\n\n唉，人世间总有很多雪雨风霜，无病是福！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1260959}, {"id": 267298, "content": "你看到的我只是我先让你看到的我 谁知道这是不是真的我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271588}, {"id": 265253, "content": "我手游队友退游的原因是她游戏打得太多，老公有意见?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461690}, {"id": 265254, "content": "网上玩王者玩的挺好，一见面差了一半，尴尬死了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262540}, {"id": 266022, "content": "微信里一个字一个字的聊天无聊到爆，二个人的聊天状态用字完全看不出来，可能你回的慢也可能别人回的慢，所以就算微信聊天也还是喜欢快发快回，不然不要文字聊天。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1267294}, {"id": 288810, "content": "微博才是我的世界，朋友圈完全就是正能量，毕竟微信都是领导。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380759}, {"id": 265268, "content": "让人很累的朋友圈，逃离朋友圈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1258452}, {"id": 291637, "content": "更依托线上的资源，回避线下", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 320215}, {"id": 265275, "content": "撒谎容易被戳穿", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262596}, {"id": 265276, "content": "你觉得你们很熟，他并不这么认为", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007288}, {"id": 265277, "content": "微信聊天印象不大好\n见面就各种好感加分\n微信聊天让人觉得冷冰冰不真实，不容易持续心动", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262600}, {"id": 265792, "content": "表情包很重要ㄟ(▔,▔)ㄏ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1183995}, {"id": 265282, "content": "在发展起来之前斩断", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262636}, {"id": 265289, "content": "虚拟网络无非是为了逃避一些现实意义的问题 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1254444}, {"id": 265294, "content": "特别没有安全感", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1210390}, {"id": 265301, "content": "网上和现实 俩人", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1260717}, {"id": 264538, "content": "发现对方有小号或拒绝透露的豆瓣、微博账号，质疑“还有多少东西是瞒着我的”", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 265306, "content": "聊天貌似有说不尽的，打电话或者见面，跟个陌生人没多大区别。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262869}, {"id": 264539, "content": "是不是可以在朋友圈晒对方照片都能引发一场小型争吵", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 264540, "content": "因为和他人的频繁互动引发对象误会", "image": null, "praise_count": 62, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 265309, "content": "网上关系很好见了面不知道说什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1011696}, {"id": 264806, "content": "“我在微博上@你的好笑段子你为啥都不回？你是不是背着我关注了别的段子手？”", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 265584, "content": "见光死？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955239}, {"id": 265332, "content": "在朋友圈里能看出谁和谁有一腿～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 988120}, {"id": 265605, "content": "各种关系都在网络上显的格外亲近 实则见面以后反而冷场 朋友也是 情侣也是 在网络上都聊的很嗨 见面以后反而不知道说些什么做些什么 更倾向于玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1265364}, {"id": 265122, "content": "我真的不想让你知道我微博", "image": null, "praise_count": 243, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1257426}, {"id": 265123, "content": "潜在问题相当多", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898852}, {"id": 265379, "content": "因为工作的原因加了微信，对方大都是男性。然后一直和你聊天，发消息，或者约你吃饭，每天如此。我一直都是礼貌的回复，有一天我不回消息，他们就会火冒三丈，然后就会说。哟，现在又不理人了，那还有什么微信可以加，删了算了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1249459}, {"id": 265124, "content": "网上聊得很热 见面却尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 470, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1080118}, {"id": 265125, "content": "qq空间的留言 ?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 758606}, {"id": 265126, "content": "不存在的，没什么亲密关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 135, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1225729}, {"id": 265127, "content": "显得面对的人更加浅薄了", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1259475}, {"id": 265128, "content": "朋友圈的图P的好看，要去见很久没见的朋友有心理负担。", "image": null, "praise_count": 80, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1261915}, {"id": 265130, "content": "发错信息撤回，结果对方看到不该看的…", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1261915}, {"id": 265133, "content": "不是所有网站的账号里的收藏点赞我都想让你知道……有一些网站我甚至都不想让你知道……", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770429}, {"id": 265134, "content": "和男朋友异国半年靠微信和Facetime还过的挺好...回来之后连着生气了4天？？？他说适应独身了？？？我俩现在微信聊的挺好...就是最好别见面....网络姻缘一线牵...男朋友不如养青蛙...", "image": null, "praise_count": 122, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1261922}, {"id": 265135, "content": "什么亲密关系，不存在的，下一个", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1058622}, {"id": 265136, "content": "网上很热络，实际见面却非常尴尬！？而且我一般都不会选择三次元面基的！？", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1261819}, {"id": 265137, "content": "相互猜忌", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1261561}, {"id": 265138, "content": "说情话变厉害起来", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1261561}, {"id": 265139, "content": "光亲密就够麻烦了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140029}, {"id": 265140, "content": "现实和网络是两个世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609486}, {"id": 265141, "content": "谎言被戳穿", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250969}, {"id": 265142, "content": "现实生活中没有表情包 不能完全表达自己的心情", "image": null, "praise_count": 93, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1252415}, {"id": 267703, "content": "完全没发隔着屏幕感受语气表情，常常误解", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1273553}]}